data.description: For any information contact CO - Lister.Welcome home! This well-maintained colonial has it all. Corner lot. Very Spacious with over 3300 SQ F. The spacious kitchen offers a pantry and breakfast bar with generous cabinet and counter space. The dining area is right off the kitchen and leads to the backyard making it perfect for entertaining. The main level living room has a gas fireplace, perfect for cozy nights! The upper level has an oversized primary suite with his and her closets. Two other generous sized bedrooms, full bath, and laundry room, Loft/2nd Family room/or office/possible for a 4th Bedroom are on the upper level. The partially finished basement offers additional finished living space with a full bathroom.The lower level with den, family room, full bathroom that walks out to level rear backyard. A lot of storage space. 2 car garage. Seller's request: please remove shoes when showing and be sure to turn off all lights and fans.
